  the  government  of  india  has  taken  a number of very good steps for the welfare of farmers  the government has made a  provision  of  rs  ten  lakh  crore  for  agriculture  loan    besides  the  government has  also  made  an  provision  of  around  48000  crore  rupees  under  mnrega  to enhance rural employment  however there is a need to strengthen rural economy so as to make villages prosperous and to ease the problems of the farmers  